org.sbml.squeezer
Interface LawListener

All Superinterfaces:
EventListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
KineticLawSelectionDialog, SBMLsqueezer
public interface LawListener
extends EventListener

Classes that implement this interface can display the progress made by KineticLawGenerator when assigning BasicKineticLaw, Parameter, UnitDefinition objects and so forth to a model.

Since:
1.1
Author:
Andreas Dräger
